WEBVTT

00:00:29.625 --> 00:00:31.684
Wakati huu wa mabadiliko makuu,

00:00:31.708 --> 00:00:35.917
Nafurahia kuwa chombo
cha ujumbe wake kwenu.

00:00:41.542 --> 00:00:43.143
Jomama Jones: Ni vipi nikikwambia

00:00:43.167 --> 00:00:45.559
itakua sawa........

00:00:45.583 --> 00:00:47.583
lakini itakuaje nkikwambia bado?

00:00:48.542 --> 00:00:51.143
Je, nikikwambia kuna majaribu mbeleni

00:00:51.167 --> 00:00:53.976
kuzidi hofu yako ya kina ?

00:00:54.000 --> 00:00:56.893
Je, nikikwambia utaanguka .....

00:00:56.917 --> 00:00:59.125
chini chini chini ?

00:01:00.000 --> 00:01:05.518
Lakini nikkiwambia 
utajishangaza?